301051.desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

301120.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.

213012.desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?
